      "rationale": "The model outputs normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) which maps directly to the clinical threshold. The transformation from CFD shear stress history to NIH uses the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model, which introduces acknowledged model-form uncertainty at high shear rates. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
